  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Compound-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across six of the seven assessed credibility factors; all thirteen factors are addressed. The overall credibility evidence is judged sufficient for regulatory submission. Decision: Accepted.",
