      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Wall shear stress distribution comparison — sub-model verification",
      "description": "Wall shear stress (WSS) distributions predicted by the CFD solver were compared against analytical Couette-flow solutions and a validated reference solver (OpenFOAM v9) on canonical geometries (parallel-plate gap, rotating cylinder). Maximum deviation from analytical solution: 1.4 %. Cross-solver agreement on the pump geometry: WSS RMS deviation 2.9 %. No separate uncertainty quantification interval was computed for this sub-model verification activity; the comparison is treated as a qualitative code-verification check only.",
      "description2": "NOTE: This validation result intentionally omits hasUncertaintyQuantification to trigger W-AL-01 (High severity)."
